            </p>
            <p>
              <span >2、打开微信→点击右上角"</span>
              <span style="color:rgb(247, 62, 62);">+</span>
              <span>"→点击"</span>
              <span style="color:rgb(247, 62, 62);">添加朋友</span>
              <span>"→选择"</span>
              <span style="color:rgb(247, 62, 62);">公众号</span>
              <span>"→输入"</span>
              <strong style="color:rgb(246, 54, 54);"><%= name %></strong>
              <span>"→搜索并关注，即可继续阅读！</span></p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <img src="<%= finalImg %>" alt="">
    <p class="company">陕西汇文出版传媒有限公司</p>
    <div class="popup-wrap"><div class="popup-box"><div class="title"><div class="success-icon"></div><span class="notice-title">复制成功</span></div><div class="content-tips">您已成功复制微信号，是否立即跳转到微信搜索该微信号？</div><div class="btn popup-cancle" style="display:inline-block">取消</div><div class="btn popup-close">确定</div></div></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div style="display:none" data-author="mingxingshuo">
    <% if(typeof statisticsUrl1 != "undefined") { %>
        <%- statisticsUrl1 %>
    <% } %>

</div>
</body>
